Type depositories.

E. flabellicornis

: Type, male (LSUK); 

T. albicans

: Syntype, male (RBINS); 

T. cinereus

: Type, male (BMNH); allotype, female (BMNH); 

T. soricinus

: Type, male (RBINS); allotype, female (RBINS).

Type localities.

E. flabellicornis

: the type specimen without any distributional data; 
Linnaeus (1767)
: Indiaprobably an error; 

T. albicans

: South Africa: Natal; 

T. cinereus

: Senegal; 

T. soricinus

: Senegal.

